George Elmo GILLIES, by His Guardian Ad Litem, George B. Gillies, v. TELLURIDE POWER COMPANY. No. 4. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 2, 1930. King & King, of Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellant. H. R. Waldo, of Salt Lake City, Utah, and Fred R. Wright, of Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, COTTERAL, and Mc-DERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed June 2, 1930, on motion of appellee.
